title: _ensnare_ - Let Us Progress To the Castle of Funk (Dualtrax & Artfx! Remix)
info:
A remix of the ingenious Chiptune "Let Us Progress To the Castle of Funk" for the upcoming album "Defend Your Ramp" written & produced by _ensnare_ (@ensnare-1) & Inspector Vector (@inspectorvector)

Remix 2013 by Dualtrax (@dualtrax) & Artfx! (@artfx)
